    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**《Knight of Noshland》**是一款设定在绚丽多彩 3D 世界中的砍杀式塔防游戏。你将扮演一名十字军骑士，亲自左右战场的走向。正面迎战无穷无尽的敌人洪流，引诱并减速敌军，最大化发挥防御塔的毁灭性威力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的主要防线是一套可建造、可升级的防御塔体系。从最初的 8 种基础塔开始，游戏中共有 20 种独特的防御塔类型，包含升级路线、分支强化以及完全形态转变，还有少量稀有变种等待玩家发现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但防御塔只是策略的一部分。你可以亲自冲入敌阵，在第三人称战斗中斩杀成群敌人。为护甲附魔、锻造元素之剑，全方位强化自身能力，将胜利的天平彻底倾向你的一方。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Noshland 本身是一个超现实的国度——一片盛产巨大可食之物的肥沃土地，却正被不断蔓延的黑暗力量所侵蚀。在这个奇幻世界中，你将面对 20 种拥有独特能力的敌人，迫使你不断调整策略，其中还包括 3 场史诗级的巨型 Boss 战。别掉以轻心……你可能会偶遇稀有的隐藏敌人变种，在意想不到的时刻改变战局。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275130/extras/7ddc4ee0a7837f2d7f1ce5f664b43b4f.webp?t=1771516271\" width=616 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275130/extras/56e822c7311ff6ba0108e60d8ef6bf85.poster.avif?t=1771516271\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275130/extras/56e822c7311ff6ba0108e60d8ef6bf85.webm?t=1771516271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275130/extras/56e822c7311ff6ba0108e60d8ef6bf85.mp4?t=1771516271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275130/extras/35b09d2a72094366c4491e9b9ce54cc1.poster.avif?t=1771516271\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275130/extras/35b09d2a72094366c4491e9b9ce54cc1.webm?t=1771516271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275130/extras/35b09d2a72094366c4491e9b9ce54cc1.mp4?t=1771516271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 种防御塔类型，包括升级、分支强化和完全形态转变</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的防御塔外观与技能</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >额外的隐藏防御塔升级变种</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275130/extras/8590643700ae4d321ede45330b8cf90f.webp?t=1771516271\" width=616 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275130/extras/5febae4262b754eecf6b93d3c0ab738b.poster.avif?t=1771516271\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275130/extras/5febae4262b754eecf6b93d3c0ab738b.webm?t=1771516271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275130/extras/5febae4262b754eecf6b93d3c0ab738b.mp4?t=1771516271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275130/extras/af9b2030ed3bdd1d282b2e798f8f19ff.poster.avif?t=1771516271\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275130/extras/af9b2030ed3bdd1d282b2e798f8f19ff.webm?t=1771516271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275130/extras/af9b2030ed3bdd1d282b2e798f8f19ff.mp4?t=1771516271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亲自参与战斗，直接影响敌人的行动路线</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >元素属性剑类升级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >附魔护甲升级</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275130/extras/e3372a2e5a5ac8d1b3c86208a2adc565.webp?t=1771516271\" width=616 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275130/extras/5fd5db8dc71f675d9ae6ac7dfef47c62.poster.avif?t=1771516271\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275130/extras/5fd5db8dc71f675d9ae6ac7dfef47c62.webm?t=1771516271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275130/extras/5fd5db8dc71f675d9ae6ac7dfef47c62.mp4?t=1771516271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275130/extras/18160742ab6797f1e4ad5076637718da.poster.avif?t=1771516271\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275130/extras/18160742ab6797f1e4ad5076637718da.webm?t=1771516271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275130/extras/18160742ab6797f1e4ad5076637718da.mp4?t=1771516271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >17 种波次敌人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >额外 3 种 Boss 敌人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >改变战术的能力与弱点设计</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的敌人角色视觉风格</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >额外的隐藏敌人变种</p></li></ul>",
